<br />No problem.  Anytime you need something tested, let me know.  It's pretty simple to drop the ROM on my pak and test away.  I'm looking forward to see how you progress with your project. 
<br />
<br />And yeah, I totally understand why you'd want to keep your game under wraps.  I'm just interested in seeing as many beginner examples as I can.  They're hard to come by, so example code is always appreciated.  I've dabbled with the NES for over a year now, with nothing substantial to show.  Nonetheless, it's fascinating to me and I'll work up enough initiative to program something one of these days.

		

