		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />On the intro screen you can see the tiles being loaded in at the top. You should mask it with a "status bar" of blank tiles, but in most cases it won't be noticeable on an NTSC TV. It will definitely show on a PAL TV, though.

		

